Big Brother 2017 , also known as Big Brother 18 , is the upcoming eighteenth series of the British reality television series Big Brother , hosted by Emma Willis and narrated by Marcus Bentley .
The series will launch on 5 June 2017 on Channel 5 in the United Kingdom .
Rylan Clark-Neal will continue to present the spin-off show Big Brother 's Bit on the Side .
It will be the seventh regular series and the nineteenth series of Big Brother in total to air on Channel 5 to date .